<TITLE>
Wiyot Language and the Wiyot Indian Tribe (Weott)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Wiyot language information and the culture, history and genealogy of the Wiyot Indians. With information and links about the Indian Island Massacre of 1860.">
<meta charset="utf-8"/> 				

